FTSE-100 Stocks Erase Gains, Trade Little Changed on Global Growth Concern

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-06-13T09:22:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/ftse-100-stocks-erase-gains-trade-little-changed-on-global-growth-concern.html
U.K. stocks erased gains, leaving
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed at 5,764.20 as of
10:21 a.m. in  London . The gauge has fallen for three straight
weeks as U.S. economic data trailed forecasts, adding to
speculation that the global economic recovery is faltering.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Adam Haigh at 
 ahaigh1@bloomberg.net  